---
import { TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';

const seo = {
  title: `Legal Information | SCI-NAD`,
  description: `Legal information for SCI-NAD, including Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.`,
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>
  <TextSection narrow>
    <h1>Legal Information</h1>

    <p>This page contains important legal information for SCI-NAD users, including our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy. Please read these documents carefully.</p>

    <h2>Terms of Service</h2>

    <p>By using SCI-NAD's services, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following terms and conditions:</p>

    <p>1. SCI-NAD provides a platform for neuroscience research and development. Users are responsible for ensuring their use of our services complies with all applicable laws and regulations.</p>

    <p>2. Users must not misuse our services or attempt to access them using a method other than the interface and instructions we provide. Users agree not to engage in any activity that interferes with or disrupts our services.</p>

    <p>3. SCI-NAD reserves the right to suspend or terminate access to our services if we reasonably believe that a user has violated these terms or is misusing our platform.</p>

    <p>4. While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, SCI-NAD is not responsible for any errors or omissions, or for the results obtained from the use of this information.</p>

    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p>
      At SCI-NAD, we are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your data with transparency:
    </p>

    <p>1. We collect and process personal data only for the purposes of providing and improving our services. This may include your name, email address, and information about your use of our platform.</p>

    <p>2. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to ensure a level of security appropriate to the risk of our data processing activities.</p>

    <p>3. We do not sell your personal data to third parties. We may share data with service providers who assist us in operating our platform, but they are obligated to keep this information confidential.</p>

    <p>4. You have the right to access, correct, or delete your personal data. For any privacy-related inquiries, please contact us at privacy@sci-nad.org.</p>

    <p>These policies may be updated from time to time. We encourage users to regularly review this page for any changes.</p>
  </TextSection>
</Layout>